' =====================================================================
' Cross-crate dependency direction (one-way, no cycles)
' =====================================================================
ENG   -[#888,dashed]-> PROTO : uses wire types
CORE  -[#888,dashed]-> PROTO : uses wire types
CORE  -[#888,dashed]-> ENG   : EngineHandle\n(channels only)
TUI   -[#888,dashed]-> PROTO : uses wire types
TUI   -[#888,dashed]-> CORE  : Core + Host\n+ capabilities
TUI   -[#888,dashed]-> UI    : ui primitives
' UI has zero internal dependencies
LUA   -[#888,dashed]-> CORE  : Host-tier smelt.* API
LUA   -[#888,dashed]-> TUI   : UiHost-tier smelt.* API

' =====================================================================
' Engine internals
' =====================================================================
EngineHandle ..> EngineEvent : event_rx
EngineHandle ..> UiCommand   : cmd_tx
ToolDispatcher ..> ToolResult : returns
ToolDispatcher ..> ToolSchema : looks up by name
Provider <|.. PA
Provider <|.. PO
Provider <|.. PCD
Provider <|.. PCP

' =====================================================================
' tui internals
' =====================================================================
Core *--> AppConfig
Core *--> Session
Core *--> Confirms
Core *--> Clipboard
Core *--> Timers
Core *--> Cells
Core *--> LuaShared
Core *--> LuaTaskRuntime
Core *--> EngineClient

HeadlessApp *--> Core
HeadlessApp ..|> Host         : impls (Ui-agnostic)

TuiApp      *--> Core
TuiApp      *--> LuaRuntime
TuiApp      *--> WellKnown
TuiApp      --> Ui            : drives compositor
TuiApp      ..|> Host         : delegates to Core
TuiApp      ..|> UiHost       : impls with Ui surface

LuaRuntime  *--> LuaShared
LuaRuntime  *--> LuaTaskRuntime

WellKnown ..> Window  : refs by WinId
Session   ..> Buffer  : transcript + prompt\nvia BufId on WellKnown

EngineClient --> EngineHandle : owns handle\nreads event stream
EngineClient ..> Confirms        : gates on is_clear()
EngineClient ..> Session         : update history,\ncosts, snapshots
EngineClient ..> Cells           : set(history),\nset(turn_complete),\nset(token_usage),\nset(message_start|end),\nset(tool_execution_start|end), …
TuiApp       ..> PromptSections   : assemble() before\nUiCommand::StartTurn
Confirms ..> EngineHandle        : PermissionDecision

Window ..> UiHost           : direct mutation\nvia &mut dyn UiHost

' Lua → tui Rust API
LDLG     -[#aa6,dashed]-> LDLGHELP        : composes via dialog.lua
LDLGHELP -[#aa6,dashed]-> Ui              : splices into splits\nor opens an Overlay
LDLGHELP -[#aa6,dashed]-> LWID            : composes widgets
LSTAT    -[#aa6,dashed]-> Window          : statusline as a Window
LSTAT    -[#aa6,dashed]-> Cells           : binds segments to cells
LPLG     -[#aa6,dashed]-> PromptSections  : register_section(name, fn)\n— P9.h system-prompt assembly
